    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine condition, featuring supple leather and that unmistakable factory-new scent. Every button, screen, and mechanical component functions flawlessly, supported by a comprehensive, documented service history. This car has been meticulously garage-kept and pampered by a single owner, ensuring it meets the highest standards of even the most discerning collector. Experience the smooth, powerful performance and uncompromised luxury of a vehicle that has been maintained with an obsessive attention to detail.",
